                    <li class="disclaimerList"> All stocks are suited for positional/swing trade and are subject to your own research before you invest. </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> We have an aim to reach all those beginners who can't afford huge amount of money to learn. </li>
                </ul><br><br>
                
                <strong style="text-decoration: underline;" class="disclaimerHeader">WHAT YOU GET AFTER JOINING US</strong><br><br>
                <ul>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Daily market view </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Daily stocks for positional trades* </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Selected videos for learning technical analysis </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Access to a private telegram group where you can discuss with other traders </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Weekly webinar for discussion of concepts </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Doubt discussion twice in a week </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Constant support on your other holdings </li>
                </ul><br>
