                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Keep learning </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Look at stock market as your secondary source of income atleast for few starting years. </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Control your emotions. </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Be disciplined. </li>
                    <li class="disclaimerList"> Finally we are here to help you. </li>
                </ul>
                <br><br><br><br>
            </p>
        </div>  
        </section>
    <section class = "footer">
        {{>footer}}
    </section>

    <script src="/loader.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/carousel.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</body>
</html>